Steps to run:

NOTE: Run these make commands from the current directory.

1. make features
    - cleans up the fasta files
    - splits them into manageable chunks
    - preocesses features using SGE on the chunks
2. make status
    - lets you check the status of the SGE jobs
    - wait for all the SGE jobs to finish
3. make svm
    - joins all the feature chunks into one big file
    - feeds them to the svm
